=head1 Unification with C<Parse::Eyapp::Unify>

When we include I<variables> in trees we have I<tree patterns>.
Unification is the problem of determining when two tree patterns C<e> and C<f>
can be made identical by substituting expressions for the I<variables> in C<e> and C<f>.


